Definition.WordDefinition: Childbirth \Child"birth\, n. The act of bringing forth a child; travail; labor. --Jer. Taylor. [1913 Webster]
childbirth n : the parturition process in human beings; having a baby; the process of giving birth to a child [syn: {childbearing}, {accouchement}, {vaginal birth}]
